Happy Birthday, my Ador

for the girl who feels like home to me
Dear Ador, You turned my ordinary days into something magical. Even when I'm tired, confused, overwhelmed one message from you makes everything feel lighter. Thank you for being gentle with me, for choosing me, and for loving me in your own soft ways. You are not just my girlfriend. You are the person who makes my world feel safe. I love you in every mood, every distance, every lifetime where I find you again. Forever yours, your stupidly-in-love partner
